<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-481] indentation of ruby classes is off by a few</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-481</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For some reason it looks like the generator indents more than it outdents in some strange way, leading to the end of the file being indented several columns&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12424560">THRIFT-481</key>
            <summary>indentation of ruby classes is off by a few</summary>
